      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and performing as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like finish with no scratches or chips, and the interior is pristine, showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a spotless engine bay and a comprehensive service history that confirms its meticulous upkeep. Prospective buyers can expect a collector-grade vehicle that offers a like-new driving experience in every possible aspect.",
