      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and she\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it for all your daily adventures or that next big road trip. It runs smoothly and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for it to start a new chapter with you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
