      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering high-revving performance via individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Mechanically sound, the dual-VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a critical point\u2014has been inspected and remains structurally integral. Power is transmitted through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains excellent damping characteristics with refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis remains composed under lateral load. While displaying minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the powertrain and drivetrain sync perfectly for an authentic M-car experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
