    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, high-performing daily driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in tires with significant tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with leather upholstery that remains supple; there is only slight, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the engine idle is whisper-quiet, the gear transitions are seamless, and the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. It has a documented service history, including a recent oil service and brake inspection. This car offers a premium driving experience for a buyer looking for a well-cared-for vehicle without the 'new car' price tag. Clean title and two sets of keys included.",
